      <div class="col-md-9">
        <h1 class="display-3 font-weight-bold">Profile</h1>
        <h5 class="font-weight-light">Thanks for completeing your profile <span id="welcome-banner"></span>. Be sure to update it frequently in order to have the most updated information.</p>
      </div>
